snippet.title: Hexocity Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
HexoCity is the first game of WAY16a ! 
‼ The demo is out on Steam (all links in the pinned comment 🔽) !!  

HexoCity is inspired by Dorfromantik and the retrofuturism of the synthwave aesthetic. It is a relaxing puzzle/city builder set up in a futuristic world where you can build your tropical archipelgao while listening to calming synths 😎🏝
